replies.body:
Latency (ping) issues are most often caused by incompatible network settings or routing issues to the server. Before we take a look at your route, we first need to ensure your local network settings are good. You can do this by working through the steps in our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if those steps caused any chance in your connection.
